    <h1>Our Community</h1>

    <p>The Washington DC metropolitan area has one of the largest and most
        active Ruby communities in the United States. This conference is
		put on by unpaid volunteers from the community to promote the
		growth of technologies like Ruby, Rails and countless others.</p>

  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Twitter Updates</h2>

    <p>Tired of checking RubyNation for updates? Check out 
	<a href="http://twitter.com/rubynation">RubyNation's Twitter account</a>.
    We post all the big news there.
    </p>

