  <div class="section">
    <h2>RubyNation Organizers</h2>

    <p>
        The RubyNation Conference is staffed by
        volunteers from this extensive Ruby community, drawn primarily from the
        membership of the Northern Virginia Ruby Users Group (<a
        href="http://www.novarug.org">NovaRUG</a>).</p>

    <h3>Our Volunteers</h3>

    <p>Our organizers are unpaid volunteers who have selflessly devoted a
        significant amount of their time and effort to make this high-quality
        regional conference a reality.</p>

    <ul class="people">
