          designer and 3D animator who is currently the lead Flash architect
          for Grab Networks. Don has over 17 years of experience using 
          computers to create art and has developed projects using a wide
          range of platforms and languages. His current home online is 
          <a href="http://www.gone3d.com">www.gone3d.com</a>. He created
          the 2009 and 2010 graphics for Rubynation.</li>

