          specializing in Java and Ruby software development. Mr. Bock is also
          the President of the Northern Virginia Java Users Group, the Editor of
          O'Reilly's <a href="http://www.onjava.com">OnJava.com</a> web site,
          and a frequent speaker on technology in venues such as the
          <em>No Fluff, Just Stuff</em> Software Symposiums.</li>
    
